        "type": "horizontalrule"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Some may recall the epic barn find ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "involving 36 Corvettes",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.corvetteheroes.com/?promo=TLC53",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " that were discovered sitting under decades of dust, each a different model year from 1953 to 1989. These epic Corvettes were once owned by renowned pop artist Peter Max who was going to use the cars as canvases to use for a series of paintings, but the project was never started so the cars have been sitting in various parking garages in New York City since 1989 collecting decades of dust and debris. One of those cars is a rare ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "first-year 1953 Chevrolet Corvette",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.corvetteheroes.com/?promo=TLC53",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Finding one of these cars today would prove a difficult task, and it would cost a small fortune if luck was on your side. Here's your chance to take home that barn find ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "1953 Chevy Corvette",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://www.corvetteheroes.com/?promo=TLC53",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " through Corvette Heroes. Tickets are just $3 each or deals are available to purchase multiple ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "tickets here ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
